Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.77,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鸣唱终演的金盏花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:01.10,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}静かに咲き誇る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:01.10,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}静静绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.78,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}憎しみも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.78,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}将憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.51,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.51,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:08.06,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その根でたくり寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:08.06,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全部寄于根茎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:11.52,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終焉を歌う金盞花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:11.52,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鸣唱终焉的金盏花
